javelin.model.world.location.unique

Class UniqueLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • javelin.model.world.WorldActor
      • javelin.model.world.location.Location
        • javelin.model.world.location.fortification.Fortification
          • javelin.model.world.location.unique.UniqueLocation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdventurersGuild, Artificer, Haxor, MercenariesGuild, PillarOfSkulls, Temple

    public abstract class UniqueLocation
extends Fortification
    An unique location is a Location that is only featured in a single location in the World map during a game. They are usually places of high power, which makes them WorldActor.impermeable by default.
    Author:
    alex
